@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cegpdo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v1
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.64 / v2 + 0.16)) + 0.33)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v0 + 0.15 / tmp + 0.08)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v1)
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.76 + v2 + 0.11)) * ((tmp + 0.20 / v1 + 0.23) - (v0 + 0.79 * v1 + 0.17)))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.50 / tmp + 0.02) - v2) * 0.67)
    data[tid] = v0
